sentences.en: Can these effects be objectively measured?
sentences.cn: 这些结果能客观地衡量吗？

sentences.en: Looked at objectively, the situation is not too bad.
sentences.cn: 客观地看，局面并不算太糟。

sentences.en: He has had time to cool down and look at what happened more objectively.
sentences.cn: 他有时间平静下来，并且更加客观地考虑发生的一切。
